request.doc:
Using a template

POST https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/http_transformation_rules 

POST_DATA {
"name":"new_file_name",
"template":"template_name"
}

Using plain text

POST https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/http_transformation_rules

POST_DATA: {
"name":"http_transformation_rules_file_name", 
"content":"http_transformation_rules_file_content" 
}
